  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Kali136-kilavi">itu varaiviṭai vaittup piriyak karutiya talaivaṉait tōḻi talaiviyāṟṟāmai kūṟic celavu vilakki varaivukaṭāyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en"></p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="Kali136">
                <l>ivartimi leṟitirai yīṇṭivan talaittakkā</l>
                <l>luvaṟunī ruyarekka ralavaṉā ṭaḷaivarit</l>
                <l>tavaliṟaṇ kaḻakattut tavirātu vaṭṭippak</l>
                <l>kavaṟuṟṟa vaṭuvēykkuṅ kāmarpūṅ kaṭaṟcērppa;</l>
                <l rend="space">muttuṟaḻ maṇalekka raḷittakkāṉ muṉṉāyam</l>
                <l>patturuvam peṟṟavaṉ maṉampōla nantiyā</l>
                <l>ḷattiṟattu nīnīṅka vaṇivāṭi yavvāyam</l>
                <l>vittattāṟ ṟōṟṟāṉpōl veytuya ruḻappavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">muṭattāḻai muṭukkaru ḷaḷittakkāl vittāya</l>
                <l>miṭaittaṅkak kaṇṭavaṉ maṉampōla nantiyāḷ</l>
                <l>koṭaittakkāy nīyāyi ṉeṟiyallāk katiyōṭi</l>
                <l>yuṭaippoti yiḻantāṉpō luṟutuya ruḻappavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">naṟuvītāḻ puṉṉaikkīḻ nayantunī yaḷittakkāṉ</l>
                <l>maṟuvitta miṭṭavaṉ maṉampōla nantiyā</l>
                <l>ḷaṟivittu nīnīṅkak karutiyāyk kapporuḷ</l>
                <l>ciṟuvitta miṭṭāṉpōṟ ceṟituya ruḻappavō;</l>
                <l rend="space">āṅku,</l>
                <l>koṇṭupalar tūṟṟuṅ kauvai yañcāy</l>
                <l>tīṇṭaṟ karuḷit tiṟaṉaṟin teḻīip</l>
                <l>pāṇṭiyañ ceyvāṉ poruḷiṉu</l>
                <l>mīṇṭuka vivaṇala mēṟuka tērē.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
                <l>O man from the coast of the sea with desirable flowers, where </l>
                <l>lines by holes where crabs play in the high dunes by the rising water,</l>
                <l>at a time when dashing waves gather, come [and] slap against the climbing boats,</l>
                <l>resemble the traces of dice, </l>
                <l corresp="1-5">as [they] throw [them] incessantly in the unfailing, cool gambling hall,</l>
                <l>At a time when you cared [for her] in dunes of sand close to pearls,</l>
                <l>as if with a mind of one who has obtained the figure of ten in the first cast, she flourished.</l>
                <l corresp="6-8">When you leave [her] on that account, ornaments fading, as if someone defeated by a throw of that cast, will they suffer hot misery?</l>
                <l>At a time when you cared [for her] in the interstices of stooped screw pines, </l>
                <l>as if with the mind of one who has seen the middle of the cast last she flourished.</l>
                <l>If you were fit to be given [her], running a way that is not customary,</l>
                <l corresp="9-12">like one who lost a treasure he possessed, will they suffer ongoing misery?</l>
                <l>At a time when you longingly cared [for her] under mastwood trees hung with fragrant blossoms, as if with the mind of one who has placed another cast she flourished.</l>
                <l>If you inform [her and] leave, for you who intended that wealth,</l>
                <l corresp="13-15">like on who as placed a small cast will they suffer dense misery?</l>
                <l>Thus,</l>
                <l>you who don’t fear the scandal taken up [and] spread by many,</l>
                <l>grace to grip ?, knowing the issue, make ? rise,</l>
                <l>more than the wealth to be made in cart-work,</l>
                <l corresp="16-20">gather her goodness [and] mount [your] chariot.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
